{{italic title}} [[File:Eros, Inside Eros.jpg| thumb| ''Eros, Inside Eros'']] '''''Eros, Inside Eros''''' (1986) is a bronze sculpture by [[Arman]].<ref>http://www.armanstudio.com/fernandez-arman-eros__inside_eros-191-3-40-it.html</ref>
It is in the [[Hirshhorn Museum and Sculpture Garden]].<ref>http://hirshhorn.si.edu/visit/collection_object.asp?key=32&subkey=3255</ref>
The artist began cutting up works in 1962; the work comments on the emptiness of the god, [[Eros]].<ref>''A Garden for Art'', Valerie J. Fletcher, OCLC 97-61991, p.82</ref>
