'''The Iziko Museums of Cape Town''' (from [[Xhosa language|isiXhosa]] Iziko is''“a [[hearth]]”'' – the traditional centre of the home where families would get together to share oral histories) — an amalgamation of 12 national museums located near the [[Cape Town]] city centre. Iziko museums spheres – natural history, social history and arts.
